As there was high system load on the whole cluster, so the jobs were running slowly . It is normal behavior on the first working day of the month.
On these days all resources (e.g. cpu, network, file system, databases) are highly utilized. Therefore it  can be that the runtimes increase significantly. 
Now the system load become normal , jobs are running fine. User has confirmed that we can close the incident.
